I tried to purchase a new monthly pass and it said my transaction was cancelled to try again. So I did. 3 times. Then I decided to wait. Tried riding the bus and my active monthly
pass was erased. Tried purchasing a daily pass and it also said transaction was
cancelled to try again. Ended up buying a daily pass cash to ride bus. I looked on my bank account and all the passes were charged. But when I log in to the Cap Metro App
it shows no available passes. How can I resolve this issue?? And May I please get a refund for my money?? Thank you!
